## User Search

<!-- example shell request -->
```shell
curl -i -H 'X-Apikey: [OPTIONAL_APIKEY]' <%= current_page.data.api_url %>/users/search?q=john
```

<!-- example response -->
<%= partial 'partials/responses/users' %>

Returns a paginated array of all users matching the search query.

### HTTP Request

`GET <%= current_page.data.api_url %>/users/search?q=`

### Query Parameters

Parameter | Default | Description
--------- | ------- | -----------
q         |         | search query
page      |         | specific page of results
per_page  | 30      | number of results per page

### Error Responses

Code | Message
---- | -------
400  | You must provide a search term!